## Additional Terms for BarathPin

### Data Usage
This application uses public postal data provided by India Post. The data is 
used solely for the purpose of helping users find postal information and is 
not used for any commercial purposes beyond the application's core functionality.

### Privacy
BarathPin respects user privacy and does not collect personal information 
beyond what is necessary for the application to function. Any data stored 
locally (such as favorites) remains on the user's device.

### Attribution
If you use this code or derive work from it, attribution to BarathPin and 
the original developers is appreciated but not required under the MIT license.
